<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 16.8667px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28.15pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">2月7日，江西省工业和信息化厅联合中共江西省委网络安全和信息化委员会办公室公布首批江西省区块链名园、名企、名品和名人名单。先锋软件股份有限公司荣登首批区块链名企名单，先锋软件集团董事局主席，学校创始人陈苏荣登区块链名人席位。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 16.8667px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28.15pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 16.8667px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28.15pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-11%2010%3A28%3A46640.jpg?Expires=2022978527&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2BJdOiVYN7KJJvp1JarErGDlu5vA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="717" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 16.8667px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28.15pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 18.4px; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">此次获评是对集团、学校在区块链研究与应用领域做出贡献的重大肯定，今后，我们将继续大力推进区块链技术发展，与和行业交流合作，持续推进企业走进校园，培养更多优秀的区块链人才。</span></p><p><br/></p>